  Locus:
    Page: 298
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Light
---
A man may wreck himself utterly in self-pleasure -- may debase his whole
nature, as it seems -- yet he fails of becoming the perfect devil, for
there is still the spark of divine light within him.
